# ============================================================
# EDUCATION CORE POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: education
scope: education.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines policy constraints for education.

## policy_rules
Education policy constrains:
- who may enroll, instruct, evaluate, or certify
- what education detail may be disclosed
- when education paths must be denied or escalated

## required_behavior
- participation/evaluation scope must be explicit
- disclosure scope must be explicit
- denial behavior must be explicit

## disclosure_matrix
- public education summary
- learner-scoped detail
- instructor/reviewer detail
- historical education detail
- denied output

## allowed_denied_matrix
- allow education action only for valid scope
- allow disclosure only for allowed actors
- deny hidden qualification widening
- deny disclosure beyond allowed scope

## escalation_rules
If education context,
evaluation basis,
or disclosure scope is unclear,
the education path must stop and escalate.
